'''黏液素'''（{{lang-en|Mucins}}，或简称'''黏素'''）是一类高[[分子量|分子量]]蛋白家族，且高度[[醣基化|醣基化]]（属于{{le|糖缀合物|glycoconjugate}}），在大部分[[后生动物|后生动物]]的[[上皮组织|上皮组织]]中都有表达。<ref name=Marin2008>{{cite book|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0070215307800068|pages=209–276|title=Molluscan Shell Proteins: Primary Structure, Origin, and Evolution|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Frédéric Marin, Gilles Luquet, Benjamin Marie, Davorin Medakovic|doi=10.1016/s0070-2153(07)80006-8|archive-date=2018-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608111009/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0070215307800068|dead-url=no}}</ref>黏液素的特色是它可以構成膠狀物；因此在體內分泌的膠狀分泌物中扮演重要角色，如：可以潤滑、協助細胞傳訊，及構築化學障壁<ref name=Marin2008/>，通常扮演身體屏障的角色。<ref name=Marin2008/>

一些黏液素参与调控生物组织的矿化，如[[软体动物|软体动物]]中[[珍珠母|珍珠母]]的形成<ref name=Marin2000>{{cite journal|title=Mucins and Molluscan Calcification MOLECULAR CHARACTERIZATION OF MUCOPERLIN, A NOVEL MUCIN-LIKE PROTEIN FROM THE NACREOUS SHELL LAYER OF THE FAN MUSSEL PINNA NOBILIS (BIVALVIA, PTERIOMORPHIA)|date=2000-07-07|doi=10.1074/jbc.m003006200|language=en|journal=Journal of Biological Chemistry|volume=275|issue=27|url=http://www.jbc.org/content/275/27/20667|pages=20667–20675|issn=0021-9258|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Frédéric Marin, Paul Corstjens, Béatrice de Gaulejac, Elizabeth de Vrind-De Jong, Peter Westbroek|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603031235/http://www.jbc.org/content/275/27/20667|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[棘皮动物|棘皮动物]]的[[钙化|钙化]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.informaworld.com/openurl?genre=article&doi=10.1080/713713622&magic=crossref%7C%7CD404A21C5BB053405B1A640AFFD44AE3|pages=5–9|title=Biomineralization: An Overview|journal=Connective Tissue Research|volume=44|issue=1|author=Adele Boskey|doi=10.1080/713713622}}</ref>，以及[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]中[[骨骼|骨骼]]的形成<ref>{{cite journal
|title=Bone sialoprotein–a mucin in disguise?
|author=RJ Midura, VC Hascall
|year=1996
|journal=Glycobiology
|doi=10.1093/glycob/6.7.677
|volume=6
|issue=7
|pages=677–81
|pmid=8953277}}</ref>。黏液素也通过与[[病原体|病原体]]结合来参与[[免疫反应|免疫反应]]，此外，过表达的黏液素蛋白，如[[MUC1|MUC1]]，也与多种[[癌症|癌症]]相关<ref name="pmid18407586">{{cite journal | author = Niv Y | title = MUC1 and colorectal cancer pathophysiology considerations | journal = World J. Gastroenterol. | volume = 14 | issue = 14 | pages = 2139–41 |date=April 2008 | pmid = 18407586 | pmc = 2703837 | doi = 10.3748/wjg.14.2139| url = | issn = }}</ref>。

Although some mucins are [[cell_membrane|membrane]]-bound due to the presence of a [[hydrophobic|hydrophobic]] membrane-spanning domain that favors retention in the [[plasma_membrane|plasma membrane]], most mucins are [[secretion|secreted]] onto [[mucosae|mucosal surfaces]] or secreted to become a component of [[saliva|saliva]].

